    "title": "Walk-in Drive Logistics Manager at Xpressbees",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Xpressbees. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Logistics Manager to strengthen our Meerut-based team.\n\nAbout Xpressbees:\nXpressbees is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Xpressbees!",
